high_descs: Walk straight to the table on the right of the TV
Pick up the newspaper on the table
Turn around and walk to the brown chair and face it
Place the newspaper on the chair seat cushion
Turn around and walk to the sofa on your right and face it
Pick up the newspaper from the sofa cushion
Turn around and walk back to the brown chair and face it
Place the newspaper on the chair seat cushion
Go the the end table in front of you.
Pick up the newspaper from the table.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right at the trash can.  Stand in front of the chair, facing the chair.
Put the newspaper on the chair.
Turn around and go to the couch on your right.
Pick up the newspaper from the couch.
Go back to the chair you put the first newspaper on.
Put the second newspaper on the chair behind the first.
anns.task_desc: Put two newspapers onto the chair.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the table next to the TV.
Pick up the newspaper on the table.
Turn and go to the fireplace and hang a right to the chair on the left.
Set the newspaper on the chair.
Walk past the coffee table on the left and take a right to the sofa.
Pick up the newspaper on the sofa.
Turn and go to the fireplace and hang a right to the chair on the left.
Set the newspaper down in the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put two newspapers in the chair.
